// Test: renderHTML Actually Working (Integration Test)
// Feature: Complete Source metaprogramming with scope interpolation
// Verifies: THE FULL VISION - template expansion with captured scope
// ============================================================================
// This test proves that the ENTIRE metaprogramming system works end-to-end:
//
// 1. Parser captures scope bindings in Source parameters (test 105 ✅)
// 2. Item transformation API works (test 106)
// 3. Comptime events execute during evaluate_comptime
// 4. renderHTML inspects source.scope.bindings
// 5. renderHTML generates runtime code with interpolations
// 6. Generated code compiles and runs
// 7. Output is correct!
